title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - France - Canadian National Vimy Memorial
description:
In this video we will fly over the Canadian National Vimy Memorial . The Canadian National Vimy Memorial is a war memorial site in France dedicated to the memory of Canadian Expeditionary Force members killed during the First World War. It also serves as the place of commemoration for Canadian soldiers of the First World War killed or presumed dead in France who have no known grave.
